  "title": "Sales Engineer (Valve / Quotations / West)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Basic $3000 - $4500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Tagore Lane</strong></li><li><strong>Working Hours: 8:45am – 6:00pm (Monday – Friday)</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits</strong></li><li><strong>Well Establish Company</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong>:</p><ul><li>Reviewing project specifications and preparing sales quotations.</li><li>To provide pre-sales and technical support to customers.</li><li>Liaising with internal departments to meet delivery dates.</li><li>To perform ad-hoc assignments if require.</li><li>To source and perform negotiation with mills/suppliers.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement</strong>:</p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Engineering or equivalent</li><li>3-5 years of sales experience in valves related products</li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p><p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
